title: Thad Jones / Mel Lewis - Central Park North (1969) SS BN
description:
(The Funky) THAD JONES/MEL LEWIS ORCHESTRA - CENTRAL PARK NORTH

01. Tow Away Zone    [4:30]
02. Quietude    [4:06]
03. Jive Samba    [8:54]
04. The Groove Merchant    [5:12]

Thad Jones - (flugelhorn), Snooky Young, Danny Moore, Jimmy Nottingham, Richard Williams (tp), Eddie Bert, Benny Powell, Jimmy Knepper (tb), Cliff Heather (b-tb), Jerome Richardson (ss, as, piccolo), Jerry Dodgion (as, cl), Joe Farrell (ts, cl), Eddie Daniels (ts, cl), Joe Temperley (bs, b-cl), Roland Hanna (p), Barry Galbraith, Sam Brown (g), Richard Davis (b, elec-b), Mel Lewis (d)
